### About

From website:

> The search feature allows you to search for Lottery grant information using certain criteria which are:

>> * by good cause area;
>> * by distributing body;
>> * by geographical area;
>> * by local authority;
>> * by parliamentary constituency;
>> * by the name of the grant recipient;
>> * by the name of the project;
>> * by grant date;
>> * by grant amount.

### Access

No bulk download, but all material is available by selecting appropriate options on the search interface.
